00:15:47,046 --> 00:15:48,816 A:middle
And from there, you're on free.

364
00:15:48,886 --> 00:15:50,586 A:middle
You can do anything
that you wish

365
00:15:50,586 --> 00:15:52,236 A:middle
with these leaderboard
set objects.

366
00:15:52,916 --> 00:15:55,476 A:middle
For instance, you can
load the leaderboards

367
00:15:55,476 --> 00:15:57,016 A:middle
that are contained
within those sets.

