00:16:11,756 --> 00:16:14,376 A:middle
And when that completion
handler is called back,

376
00:16:14,376 --> 00:16:17,316 A:middle
you'll be provided an NSArray
of GK Leaderboard instances.

377
00:16:18,246 --> 00:16:20,796 A:middle
And now I'm assuming that
you're already familiar

378
00:16:20,796 --> 00:16:23,136 A:middle
with GK Leaderboard
objects, from this point,

379
00:16:23,136 --> 00:16:24,636 A:middle
you can treat these objects just

