00:17:03,036 --> 00:17:03,686 A:middle
within your game.

396
00:17:04,246 --> 00:17:07,576 A:middle
So that's Leaderboard Sets.

397
00:17:08,006 --> 00:17:11,435 A:middle
Again, it's-- you can think of
them as a tagging architecture.

398
00:17:11,496 --> 00:17:15,185 A:middle
It allows you to group multiple
leaderboards into a set.

399
00:17:15,546 --> 00:17:17,156 A:middle
A single leaderboard
can be contained

400
00:17:17,156 --> 00:17:18,526 A:middle
within many different sets.

401
00:17:19,366 --> 00:17:21,866 A:middle
An important thing that I
wish to pint out here is

