406
00:17:36,516 --> 00:17:39,086 A:middle
So let's move on to the next new
thing with leaderboards today,

407
00:17:40,176 --> 00:17:41,556 A:middle
Most Recent Score Leaderboards.

408
00:17:42,356 --> 00:17:44,726 A:middle
So you're all probably
already familiar

409
00:17:44,726 --> 00:17:46,766 A:middle
with how leaderboards
work within Game Center,

