X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00,000

440
00:19:01,216 --> 00:19:03,376 A:middle
or your legendary
RPG Heroes game.

441
00:19:03,986 --> 00:19:06,846 A:middle
You could do win/lose
percentage or even, you know,

442
00:19:06,846 --> 00:19:10,496 A:middle
simpler things like batting
average or golf strokes or OPS.

443
00:19:10,846 --> 00:19:12,356 A:middle
Really, it's entirely up to you.

444
00:19:13,186 --> 00:19:15,596 A:middle
And setting up a Most
Recent Score Leaderboard

